pdate Progress\\\"\\n4. \\\"4th Phase: Final (Presentation)\\\"\\nAI: Sure thing! To add the four phases to your Google Calendar I’ll need the dates for each one (and whether you’d like them as all‑day events). Could you let me know the start and end dates for:\\n\\n1. **1st Phase: Literature Review**  \\n2. **2nd Phase: Project Proposal**  \\n3. **3rd Phase: Update Progress**  \\n4. **4th Phase: Final (Presentation)**  \\n\\nOnce I have that, I’ll create the events for you.\\nHuman:  Please create 4 Google Calendar events\\nfor my project:\\n1. \\\"1st Phase: Literature Review\\\"\\nApril 7 to April 20, 2026\\n2. \\\"2nd Phase: Project Proposal\\\"\\nApril 21 to May 4, 2026\\n3. \\\"3rd Phase: Update Progress\\\"\\nMay 5 to May 18, 2026\\n4. \\\"4th Phase: Final (Presentation)\\\"\\nMay 19 to May 25, 2026\\n\\n\\nEach should be an all-day event.\\nAI: Calling Create_an_event_in_Google_Calendar with input: {\\\"End\\\":\\\"2026-05-25T00:00:00+07:00\\\",\\\"Start\\\":\\\"2026-05-19T00:00:00+07:00\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"fc_2c106a59-7d58-42ac-b3ba-8a2e88594d50\\\"}[{\\\"id\\\":\\\"fc_2c106a59-7d58-42ac-b3ba-8a2e88594d50\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Create_an_event_in_Google_Calendar\\\",\\\"args\\\":{\\\"End\\\":\\\"2026-05-25T00:00:00+07:00\\\",\\\"Start\\\":\\\"2026-05-19T00:00:00+07:00\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"fc_2c106a59-7d58-42ac-b3ba-8a2e88594d50\\\"},\\\"type\\\":\\\"tool_call\\\"}]\\nTool: Create_an_event_in_Google_Calendar, [{\\\"id\\\":\\\"p3pa0d81lgp4ulps89k538cnj8\\\",\\\"start\\\":{\\\"dateTime\\\":\\\"2026-05-19T00:00:00+07:00\\\",\\\"timeZone\\\":\\\"Asia/Bangkok\\\"},\\\"end\\\":{\\\"dateTime\\\":\\\"2026-05-25T00:00:00+07:00\\\",\\\"timeZone\\\":\\\"Asia/Bangkok\\\"},\\\"creator\\\":{\\\"email\\\":\\\"st126235@ait.asia\\\",\\\"self\\\":true},\\\"organizer\\\":{\\\"email\\\":\\\"st126235@ait.asia\\\",\\\"self\\\":true},\\\"created\\\":\\\"2026-03-29T20:55:52.000Z\\\",\\\"updated\\\":\\\"2026-03-29T20:55:52.401Z\\\",\\\"etag\\\":\\\"\\\\\\\"3549635504803710\\\\\\\"\\\",\\